data.text: Werewolf bf, eyes yellow with slit pupils: stop tickling me I'm trying to transform into a wolf

@stackthelions We had to clasp our hands on top of our heads to mimic a yamaka while our eyes were closed. They sprinkled water on us while we did this. This was the final step before you and the rabbi came out with a certificate for me.

On a semi-unrelated note, I also went to European oaks park but it got shut down for the summer because of vandalism. I was so pissed. It was so hard to convince everyone to go in the first place. It was also in the middle of the woods. The entire dream was a camping trip.

@stackthelions you were there for all the meetings I had to go to.  I don't remember the specifics of these but there were several people and we all stood in a circle. No one was allowed to know who was joining and also I feel like there was a wheel of Fortune type deal goin on.
